            "name": "Caligni Dancer",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Caligni dancers serve as intermediaries between caligni clans.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 15",
